WEBVTT

00:14.310 --> 00:18.030
Do you think you can save him?

00:18.280 --> 00:19.420
What?

00:21.150 --> 00:22.840
I need to do his operation first.

00:23.170 --> 00:24.770
But it’s bleeding in his biliary system...

00:24.770 --> 00:26.160
No need to explain.

00:26.160 --> 00:29.000
Tell me if you can save him or not.

00:29.000 --> 00:30.340
As a doctor.

00:32.960 --> 00:34.890
You idiot! What do you think you're doing?

00:34.890 --> 00:35.930
Answer me!

00:38.500 --> 00:39.510
I can save him.

00:47.740 --> 00:48.560
Then save him.

01:02.900 --> 01:04.959
Let’s move him to the OR.

01:06.890 --> 01:10.280
Get back! I'm telling you for the last time.

01:10.280 --> 01:13.140
As of now, protecting the medical team and the patient

01:13.860 --> 01:15.110
is our priority.

01:16.440 --> 01:20.360
Everyone, stand in front a line.

01:27.810 --> 01:31.210
From this moment on, you can open fire at

01:32.229 --> 01:33.430
anyone who threatens these people.

01:34.060 --> 01:36.150
Look, Captain!

01:36.150 --> 01:38.870
You'd better know exactly what you're doing.

01:38.870 --> 01:40.479
You do your job.

01:40.479 --> 01:42.850
The doctor will save our patient

01:42.850 --> 01:46.570
and I will protect them.

01:49.830 --> 01:51.100
Let’s move him now.

02:38.980 --> 02:41.190
The VIP patient is in the OR.

02:41.520 --> 02:42.400
Our soldiers are in a standoff

02:42.400 --> 02:43.380
with Chairman Mubarat's Secret Service Team.

02:43.380 --> 02:44.930
They're pointing guns at each other. -

02:44.930 --> 02:45.860
From the perspective of medicine,

02:45.860 --> 02:47.750
our medical team made the right choice.

02:47.750 --> 02:51.290
It's not important whether the medical team made the right choice or not.

02:51.290 --> 02:54.100
This guy is President Mubarat of the Arab League.

02:54.100 --> 02:56.240
What if things go wrong?

02:56.240 --> 02:58.220
Any wrong, our government

02:58.220 --> 03:00.440
will go against the entire Arab world.

03:01.760 --> 03:04.360
Let's start the operation. Scalpel.

03:12.390 --> 03:14.920
You crazy idiots! Stop now!

03:19.350 --> 03:21.110
Yoo Shi Jin! Seo Dae Young!

03:22.870 --> 03:24.400
Why isn't anyone answering?

03:35.950 --> 03:37.450
Sir! All the Special Forces soldiers are standing by

03:37.450 --> 03:38.829
on the drill ground in full kit.

03:38.829 --> 03:40.540
DEFCON1 in the Taeback Unit.

03:40.540 --> 03:41.930
I can hear that!

03:42.390 --> 03:44.210
I know. Get the car ready!

03:45.570 --> 03:46.230
Sir!

03:49.390 --> 03:51.540
You idiots! Because of you,

03:51.540 --> 03:53.340
FPCON 1 is in effect.

03:53.340 --> 03:54.810
War might break out.

03:56.470 --> 03:59.860
Anyone who's listening to me! Deliver my message to Yoo Shi Jin.

03:59.860 --> 04:01.980
Get the doctor out of the room, stop the operation immediately

04:01.980 --> 04:03.750
and hand the patient over to his team.

04:03.750 --> 04:05.700
Or I'll kill those

04:05.700 --> 04:08.630
disobeying military orders!

04:12.510 --> 04:14.040
Once you start, there's no turning back.

04:14.530 --> 04:15.330
If you've changed your mind...

04:15.330 --> 04:16.329
Doctor Song, this one here.

04:18.180 --> 04:20.360
It's a subcostal incision, right?

04:20.360 --> 04:22.440
The history sheet didn’t mention any operation.

04:23.040 --> 04:26.200
It means, except for the facts we have found out,

04:26.200 --> 04:28.400
we can't trust anything in the sheet.

04:28.400 --> 04:31.120
So this is an extremely dangerous operation.

04:31.120 --> 04:34.200
For the patient, for us, and for the soldiers outside…

04:34.200 --> 04:35.240
If I don't do it because it's dangerous,

04:35.240 --> 04:36.850
he'll die.

04:37.560 --> 04:39.700
As doctors, we have no other option.

04:49.140 --> 04:50.080
Let's begin.

05:02.490 --> 05:03.720
You know,

05:03.720 --> 05:06.230
for 1.6 billion Arabs

05:06.230 --> 05:09.250
you are pointing the knife on the heart of peace.

05:09.250 --> 05:15.240
The doctor is just operating on a patient who needs surgery.

05:16.830 --> 05:17.820
As I guessed,

05:17.820 --> 05:20.240
and now I’ve confirmed,

05:20.240 --> 05:21.300
the patient had a gallbladder operation.

05:21.300 --> 05:23.150
The tissue is all adhering together.

05:23.150 --> 05:24.800
Let's take care of that first.

05:25.150 --> 05:26.350
One by one.

05:27.380 --> 05:28.730
Cautery snare!

05:34.120 --> 05:35.860
Blood pressure's dropping fast.

05:35.860 --> 05:37.210
He's bleeding too much.

05:37.210 --> 05:38.480
Give him more blood. Quick!

05:40.650 --> 05:43.409
-Blood pressure's dropping more. –What should we do?

05:43.409 --> 05:44.659
If things go wrong,

05:44.659 --> 05:46.070
we'll all die.

05:46.940 --> 05:48.350
I'm a father now.

05:49.490 --> 05:54.590
Anything goes wrong, you will pay for this.

05:58.159 --> 06:00.220
Inshallah!

06:01.080 --> 06:03.070
It's all up to Allah.

06:09.010 --> 06:10.180
This isn't working.

06:10.530 --> 06:12.050
We don't have time.

06:12.050 --> 06:13.230
The most important thing is to

06:13.230 --> 06:14.910
clean up this area here quickly, and…

06:14.910 --> 06:16.940
Doctor Song, more blood.

06:18.650 --> 06:20.640
We can deal with the amount of blood he's losing.

06:20.640 --> 06:24.570
Let’s get rid of the adhesions first and stop the bleeding.

06:25.710 --> 06:27.150
Let's do as

06:27.150 --> 06:28.680
what we originally planned.

06:28.970 --> 06:29.580
But...

06:29.580 --> 06:32.640
Stop whining and go get about 10 RBC packs.

06:34.800 --> 06:35.820
Let’s do it again.

06:39.830 --> 06:41.690
Let's keep going.

06:54.900 --> 06:57.610
-How's it going? -The operation is still going on.

07:05.850 --> 07:07.600
I think the Arab doctor has arrived.

07:27.220 --> 07:29.430
Good.

07:29.430 --> 07:30.940
We’ve taken care of the aneurysm.

07:31.120 --> 07:32.550
His blood pressure is stabilizing.

07:43.430 --> 07:45.260
Good. Let's

07:45.260 --> 07:46.670
clean up the area

07:46.670 --> 07:47.640
and suture the blood vessels.

08:04.500 --> 08:07.860
Seems like the operations went well.

08:07.860 --> 08:09.910
It'll leave a scar.

08:09.910 --> 08:11.920
if I had the right chart.

08:11.920 --> 08:14.170
It could have been better

08:14.170 --> 08:15.390
Well, the patient still needs to wake up

08:15.390 --> 08:19.210
to call the surgery a success.

08:19.810 --> 08:22.290
I'd still be worried if I were you.

08:22.290 --> 08:23.750
If I'd just sat around

08:23.750 --> 08:25.740
and worried and did nothing,

08:25.740 --> 08:26.910
you'd have a dead body now.

08:26.910 --> 08:29.490
He could still die.

08:32.570 --> 08:33.870
I know that.

08:39.940 --> 08:40.820
Are you okay?

08:45.580 --> 08:47.560
I'll keep an eye on him. Go get some rest.

08:48.100 --> 08:48.990
I'm okay.

08:50.920 --> 08:51.880
I'm just hungry.

08:53.600 --> 08:57.030
Take Ms. Ha and Ms. Choi, you go to eat something.

08:57.030 --> 08:58.650
Come back and switch places with me.

08:59.200 --> 08:59.980
Okay.

09:01.410 --> 09:02.830
By the way,

09:04.370 --> 09:05.600
what if he doesn't wake up?

09:08.650 --> 09:09.910
There'll be a case report

09:09.910 --> 09:13.230
about hepatic artery aneurysms

09:16.200 --> 09:18.210
and world history will change a little.

09:19.580 --> 09:22.030
Can something go wrong while he's in recovery?

09:22.550 --> 09:25.780
The operation was successful.

09:25.780 --> 09:27.800
But if he starts bleeding again...

09:27.800 --> 09:29.190
I don't need an explanation.

09:29.570 --> 09:31.430
We need to wait and see what happens.

09:32.860 --> 09:33.540
We avoided

09:33.540 --> 09:35.780
the worst-case scenario of exchanging fire,

09:36.300 --> 09:37.260
but we need to deal with them diplomatically.

09:40.040 --> 09:43.730
Don't you think you should do something to the leader?

09:54.240 --> 09:56.650
Commander here. Connect me to the signal corps.

10:00.060 --> 10:01.250
Alpha Team Seo Dae Young, can you hear me?

10:01.250 --> 10:03.360
This is Commander Yun.

10:04.030 --> 10:06.090
Yes, sir! Sergeant Seo Dae Young!

10:07.250 --> 10:12.220
Detain Captain Yoo Shi Jin for insubordination.

10:12.220 --> 10:14.070
Confine him to the barracks.

10:21.460 --> 10:23.440
I know. As your superior,

10:23.440 --> 10:25.250
I'm proud of you.

10:25.250 --> 10:26.570
Thank you.

10:27.640 --> 10:30.060
However, an order is an order.

10:30.060 --> 10:31.220
Carry it out.

10:57.230 --> 10:59.000
Corporal Gong Chul Ho!

11:03.530 --> 11:07.370
Captain Yoo Shi Jin! You're being charged with insubordination

11:07.370 --> 11:10.010
and will be detained in the barracks.

11:16.050 --> 11:21.000
I'm not running off. I've been summoned.

11:28.140 --> 11:31.430
Take care of things.

11:48.650 --> 11:50.800
Is he here to watch us?

11:51.230 --> 11:54.310
I don't think he's here to eat cup noodles with us.

11:59.880 --> 12:01.130
It hasn't been three minutes yet.

12:02.560 --> 12:06.930
No. I can't remember how much gauze was left.

12:07.890 --> 12:09.490
I hope I didn't

12:09.490 --> 12:11.270
leave some in his belly.

12:12.570 --> 12:15.400
That's not funny.

12:16.190 --> 12:17.320
Besides,

12:17.320 --> 12:18.550
Ms. Ha is really thorough...

12:18.550 --> 12:21.550
Should I go and check again? How many were there originally?

12:21.550 --> 12:23.240
What are you talking about?

12:27.820 --> 12:29.130
On the commander’s orders,

12:29.130 --> 12:31.860
you'll be detained in this supply storehouse

12:31.860 --> 12:33.550
to wait for further orders.

12:36.820 --> 12:38.940
I'd rather stay in the food storehouse.

12:44.330 --> 12:45.270
Sir!

12:47.610 --> 12:48.930
Seo Dae Young. Get out!

12:51.260 --> 12:52.330
Sir!

13:00.080 --> 13:01.410
You crazy idiot!

13:01.770 --> 13:05.600
The captain is locked up in here with his army in a mess.

13:05.600 --> 13:06.450
I'm sorry, sir!

13:06.450 --> 13:09.200
Why did you do that then?

13:09.910 --> 13:11.320
Do you know how many people are in trouble

13:11.320 --> 13:12.990
because of what you've done?

13:13.210 --> 13:15.910
-I have no excuse to offer. -Of course not.

13:19.400 --> 13:21.830
If you can follow the order, you'll get promoted

13:21.830 --> 13:23.480
and receive a military decoration.

13:23.890 --> 13:25.300
You are suffering from your own actions.

13:28.030 --> 13:29.040
I have no regrets.

13:30.620 --> 13:33.340
I made the decision

13:34.940 --> 13:38.440
and I take full responsibility.

13:40.940 --> 13:44.790
You’d better do.

13:49.590 --> 13:50.870
Where's Captain Yoo?

13:50.870 --> 13:53.370
He's been locked up. He's not allowed to have visitors.

13:53.370 --> 13:55.250
For five minutes. Please?

14:00.750 --> 14:01.880
Seo Dae Young,

14:01.880 --> 14:03.230
where's that crazy doctor

14:03.230 --> 14:05.120
called Kang Mo Yeon?

14:05.120 --> 14:06.050
Go get her.

14:06.050 --> 14:07.460
I want to meet her.

14:08.550 --> 14:09.690
When the president wakes up...

14:09.690 --> 14:13.670
I'm Kang Mo Yeon.

14:18.930 --> 14:21.150
How’s the VIP? Is he still unconscious?

14:21.630 --> 14:22.750
We're watching him.

14:22.750 --> 14:26.410
That's not what I want to hear. What if he doesn't wake up?

14:28.550 --> 14:32.190
It’s rational as a doctor when I diagnosed and treated him.

14:34.000 --> 14:35.470
You seem so proud.

14:36.010 --> 14:37.100
If you get fired,

14:37.100 --> 14:38.560
you can start your own clinic.

14:38.560 --> 14:40.310
Because you're a famous doctor.

14:42.140 --> 14:44.250
You don't care what you did to Yoo Shi Jin.

14:45.860 --> 14:47.070
His career as a soldier

14:47.070 --> 14:50.200
for the past several years has been completely ruined.

14:51.090 --> 14:52.180
If the president can’t make it,

14:52.180 --> 14:54.390
the rest of his life will be ruined,

14:54.390 --> 14:57.090
thanks to your rational decision.

15:04.630 --> 15:05.700
Please make sure he wakes up.

15:06.930 --> 15:10.580
That way, you and I will survive.

15:14.000 --> 15:15.100
Please.

15:25.410 --> 15:26.250
Sir!

15:32.750 --> 15:34.200
About the president's status...

15:34.200 --> 15:35.090
Stop.

15:35.440 --> 15:36.480
I don't want to see you.

15:36.480 --> 15:37.900
Pack your stuff and go to the airport.

15:38.240 --> 15:39.710
You're still being transferred.

15:39.710 --> 15:42.520
I know that, but the captain is suspended

15:42.520 --> 15:43.250
and I'm the...

15:43.250 --> 15:45.980
Why couldn't you stop him earlier?

15:46.580 --> 15:48.370
Do you want to be punished for defiance?

15:50.450 --> 15:52.870
Sergeant Choi will be in charge temporarily.

15:53.790 --> 15:55.540
You're going back to Korea, as ordered.

15:55.540 --> 15:56.390
Are you clear?

15:56.390 --> 15:57.470
Yes, sir!

16:01.330 --> 16:04.060
One more thing. Listen to me carefully.

16:04.850 --> 16:07.040
When you get back and are investigated,

16:07.040 --> 16:09.800
Yoo Shi Jin is responsible for everything.

16:10.690 --> 16:11.790
Don't forget that.

16:14.280 --> 16:15.400
Go!

16:35.430 --> 16:36.760
Are you leaving now?

16:36.760 --> 16:38.940
I'm leaving at 21:00.

16:41.100 --> 16:42.840
You don't want to stay?

16:43.280 --> 16:45.590
Why don't you try to disobey the order?

16:47.700 --> 16:51.240
I want to stay, but this is an order.

16:54.780 --> 16:57.020
I'm sorry that I have to leave at the time.

16:58.090 --> 16:59.390
I'm here to report my transfer.

17:01.180 --> 17:03.590
I've been suspended. I’m not your superior anymore.

17:04.750 --> 17:06.230
Don't bother.

17:09.260 --> 17:13.349
The orders that my superior gave me today

17:13.349 --> 17:15.060
were all correct.

17:16.579 --> 17:18.890
And the orders that my superior

17:18.890 --> 17:22.050
gave me today were honorable.

17:24.270 --> 17:26.829
I'll see you back in our homeland, sir.

17:30.730 --> 17:35.170
I'll buy you a drink. Three days straight.

17:47.550 --> 17:49.740
Sir! From May 24th, 2015,

17:49.740 --> 17:51.890
Sergeant Seo Dae Young

17:51.890 --> 17:54.390
was ordered to the Special Forces Command.

17:54.390 --> 17:57.320
Over, Sir!

17:58.920 --> 18:00.540
Good.

18:11.010 --> 18:13.730
20:50. You have 10 minutes.

18:23.070 --> 18:26.440
It's Kang Mo Yeon.

18:30.970 --> 18:32.020
Let's go.

18:32.020 --> 18:33.880
Yes, sir.

18:55.620 --> 18:57.760
I'm glad you're here.

18:59.800 --> 19:00.860
Are you here to visit me?

19:08.500 --> 19:09.600
I'm sorry.

19:10.670 --> 19:12.930
You don’t have to.

19:15.300 --> 19:20.150
The patient hasn’t woken up.

19:22.290 --> 19:27.230
You're worried about too many men.

19:28.540 --> 19:29.900
Save your feelings.

19:30.440 --> 19:34.310
From now on, you can only worry about me.

19:39.490 --> 19:40.760
Just now I saw the moment.

19:41.860 --> 19:43.920
I think what you said in the past was true.

19:46.500 --> 19:47.990
What do you mean?

19:49.570 --> 19:51.580
You were really sexy in the OR.

19:51.580 --> 19:52.960
Why did you do that?

19:55.480 --> 20:00.300
You had a choice.

20:00.780 --> 20:02.890
It didn't have to come down to this.

20:02.890 --> 20:04.460
I told you.

20:04.460 --> 20:07.700
It's my philosophy that I protect

20:07.700 --> 20:09.480
beautiful ladies, senior citizens, and children.

20:10.900 --> 20:12.220
I had a beautiful lady and

20:13.500 --> 20:14.920
also a senior citizen in front of me.

20:15.930 --> 20:17.220
But I can’t protect them.

20:23.920 --> 20:25.280
You were very brave today.

20:28.510 --> 20:29.800
You know?

20:38.880 --> 20:39.890
Are you crying?

20:46.430 --> 20:50.340
Are you okay in there? You need anything?

20:50.340 --> 20:51.950
Can I get some C4 and RDX?

20:53.580 --> 20:54.940
What's that?

20:54.940 --> 20:56.560
Explosives.

20:56.910 --> 20:58.690
I was okay

20:59.330 --> 21:01.470
but now I want to blow up this door out.

21:02.070 --> 21:02.980
Because of someone.

21:09.950 --> 21:10.940
Even in this moment,

21:10.940 --> 21:12.590
you’re still kidding me.

21:13.950 --> 21:18.450
It's hard, but I can pull it off.

21:19.790 --> 21:21.200
I

21:28.090 --> 21:29.280
I think time's up.

21:36.660 --> 21:40.770
Here. I thought you might need it.

21:47.590 --> 21:49.010
I have to go.

21:49.730 --> 21:51.100
Thank you.

21:53.660 --> 21:55.870
It's exactly what I need.

23:33.350 --> 23:35.660
He is okay now.

23:37.770 --> 23:39.480
What are you doing? Move!

23:40.180 --> 23:41.770
Hey! He's just a kid.

23:42.220 --> 23:46.390
What's wrong?

23:47.640 --> 23:50.300
Mr. President, can you see me?

23:53.150 --> 23:55.280
Follow my finger.

24:02.140 --> 24:03.610
He awakes!

24:04.710 --> 24:05.710
I thought I was going to die.

24:06.330 --> 24:08.390
I thought I'd die at the age of 37

24:08.390 --> 24:10.010
in a foreign country.

24:10.650 --> 24:12.730
The patient survived and we survive.

24:12.730 --> 24:14.240
I'm so relieved.

24:14.240 --> 24:15.500
My parents are rich, but not rich enough

24:15.500 --> 24:17.450
to deal with this situation.

24:18.190 --> 24:20.110
Right. Even your parents couldn't fix it.

24:20.510 --> 24:22.270
This is the second time in my career that

24:22.270 --> 24:24.320
I've been so scared in the OR.

24:24.980 --> 24:26.030
When was the first time?

24:26.030 --> 24:27.930
When I operated for her mother,

24:27.930 --> 24:30.850
I was so nervous that something might go wrong.

24:33.430 --> 24:35.200
Let's go. The chairman is leaving.

24:38.030 --> 24:41.190
Attention! Salute!

25:01.110 --> 25:02.740
At ease!

25:06.270 --> 25:07.340
The president is moving with his doctor.

25:07.340 --> 25:09.270
to the city.

25:09.660 --> 25:13.290
The operation was a success and they got along well.

25:14.100 --> 25:15.060
All are gone.

25:16.120 --> 25:17.070
Glad to hear that.

25:17.870 --> 25:19.250
Don't worry.

25:19.250 --> 25:20.350
Have a safe trip.

25:22.070 --> 25:23.800
I have a whiny kid here.

25:23.800 --> 25:25.200
Let me put you on speakerphone.

25:27.080 --> 25:27.690
This is Private Kim Ki Bum,

25:27.690 --> 25:29.230
in the service of communications.

25:29.590 --> 25:31.600
How can you do that to me?

25:32.910 --> 25:34.790
How can you leave me like this?

25:35.210 --> 25:39.830
I left. The electronic dictionary is yours.

25:39.830 --> 25:42.370
Study hard for your test.

25:42.370 --> 25:45.890
Sergeant Choi, make sure he studies hard.

25:45.890 --> 25:47.280
Okay. I’ll keep an eye on him.

25:48.510 --> 25:49.340
Yes, sir.

25:49.850 --> 25:52.500
Good. Fighting. I got to go.

26:37.520 --> 26:39.650
This is the one that I came here for.

26:40.760 --> 26:42.560
But he showed up here. What should I do?

26:44.830 --> 26:46.320
Where are you go?

26:47.880 --> 26:49.450
Run away again?

26:50.770 --> 26:52.990
I asked if you were running away from me.

26:58.520 --> 27:09.430
Sergeant Seo Dae Young. I was ordered to return to the homeland…

27:13.560 --> 27:14.890
Tell me that this is a strategic retreat.

27:17.440 --> 27:19.190
Tell me to wait.

27:21.890 --> 27:24.980
Tell me that you'll come back whatever it takes.

27:33.260 --> 27:34.440
There are lots of mosquitoes.

27:35.470 --> 27:37.170
Keep your uniform on even if it's really hot.

28:01.520 --> 28:03.770
What's this?

28:06.230 --> 28:08.000
What do you want me to do?

28:08.600 --> 28:11.020
I want you to take care of yourself.

28:18.250 --> 28:19.300
Ma'am!

28:24.310 --> 28:27.850
Why did you hug me and touch me?

28:28.610 --> 28:30.640
If you touch me, be responsible for that. Asshole.

28:31.890 --> 28:34.120
You said I can't be happy if I still love you.

28:34.120 --> 28:36.070
You were so kind to your ex.

28:37.560 --> 28:39.800
Why can’t you do that to me?

28:45.020 --> 28:48.540
Did you love her with all your heart?

28:48.540 --> 28:50.090
Why do you ask?

28:50.990 --> 28:54.170
It decides how far the revenge goes.

28:55.220 --> 28:58.070
I promised her that I'd make her happy.

29:00.480 --> 29:01.570
Ruining her wedding

29:01.570 --> 29:03.190
won't make her happy at all, right?

29:04.130 --> 29:06.340
If she still has feelings for me, she can't be happy.

29:09.060 --> 29:15.630
You're not here to hurt her. You came here to comfort her?

29:26.840 --> 29:28.030
How did you...

29:28.030 --> 29:30.040
I was wondering whom you’re going to marry.

29:30.770 --> 29:32.360
I saw him.

29:32.360 --> 29:33.790
You didn't talk to him, did you?

29:33.790 --> 29:34.840
I might on my way out.

29:34.840 --> 29:36.430
Dae Young, please...

29:39.720 --> 29:43.350
Hello. Congratulations on your wedding.

29:43.810 --> 29:44.530
Who's she?

29:44.530 --> 29:46.940
I thought I should say hi.

29:47.490 --> 29:49.220
Thank you for leaving him.

29:49.850 --> 29:51.930
I'm his girlfriend.

29:53.120 --> 29:54.900
Anyway, how should I address you?

29:54.900 --> 29:57.400
You can call me Doctor Yoon.

29:57.760 --> 29:59.130
I'm a doctor.

29:59.800 --> 30:01.140
Is she really your girlfriend?

30:01.140 --> 30:02.350
Anyway.

30:07.960 --> 30:08.910
Thanks to her.

30:08.910 --> 30:11.490
I don't think I'll miss you anymore.

30:13.100 --> 30:15.660
You're marrying him.

30:15.660 --> 30:17.320
I want you to be happy.

30:18.530 --> 30:22.500
Congratulations. I mean it.

30:31.530 --> 30:32.410
Do you regret it?

30:34.440 --> 30:35.990
No. I feel free.

30:40.240 --> 30:41.810
I feel a little regretful.

30:41.810 --> 30:43.300
What do you mean?

30:43.560 --> 30:45.270
I don't know.

30:45.700 --> 30:47.450
It’s weird.

30:49.750 --> 30:51.780
Anyway, I did my part.

30:51.780 --> 30:54.730
Don't forget to tell Yoo Shi Jin that we're seeing each other.

30:54.730 --> 30:55.700
Don't worry.

31:02.590 --> 31:05.980
I said I wouldn't marry Yoo Shi Jin.

31:05.980 --> 31:07.970
I didn't say I won’t marry all my life.

31:08.720 --> 31:10.810
What did you tell people?

31:10.810 --> 31:15.090
I said I was going out with Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo.

31:15.090 --> 31:16.680
That's all I said.

31:17.500 --> 31:19.650
Then the camp has the rumor that

31:19.650 --> 31:22.400
you and I slept together?

31:23.360 --> 31:25.150
I guess they have good imaginations.

31:27.940 --> 31:30.400
Sergeant Seo, do you think this is funny?

31:32.010 --> 31:33.240
It's rather amusing, yes.

31:36.270 --> 31:38.490
You're completely okay with this?

31:38.490 --> 31:39.610
How can you men think that

31:39.610 --> 31:40.980
dating is sleeping?

31:40.980 --> 31:43.770
A man’s thought. Don't worry about it.

31:43.770 --> 31:46.910
If you love someone, then sleep...

31:49.050 --> 31:50.850
-Sleep what? -My mistake.

31:50.850 --> 31:52.530
You can't fool me.

31:52.530 --> 31:54.900
Is that what you men all thinking about?

31:55.070 --> 31:57.550
For me, I can only sleep with…

31:59.180 --> 32:00.930
We must lose.

32:05.390 --> 32:06.080
I don’t know how to win,

32:06.080 --> 32:07.340
but I know how to get even.

32:08.230 --> 32:09.450
How?

32:09.450 --> 32:11.550
We can make the rumor true.

32:12.470 --> 32:14.120
Make the rumor ture...

32:16.680 --> 32:18.280
How dare you!

32:18.280 --> 32:19.250
Are you okay?

32:20.000 --> 32:22.270
-Unbelievable you’re this kind. –I’m sorry.

32:22.270 --> 32:23.680
How dare you!

32:25.920 --> 32:26.920
It’s reported that Lieutenant Yoon Myung Joo

32:26.920 --> 32:29.230
has arrived at Taebaek Unit in Uruk.

32:29.650 --> 32:31.500
And Sergeant Seo Dae Young

32:31.500 --> 32:33.160
left the Uruk Airport at 13:00.

32:36.040 --> 32:37.590
It's the Blue House.

32:37.590 --> 32:38.660
Put it through.

32:43.770 --> 32:46.100
-This is Commander Yoon. -This is Lee Hansu.

32:46.600 --> 32:49.040
Just now, the Arab League asked for our cooperation

32:49.040 --> 32:51.880
regarding the president's surgery, unofficially.

32:53.380 --> 32:55.140
In a nutshell,

32:55.720 --> 32:57.810
they insisted the operation never happened.

32:57.810 --> 33:00.640
Therefore he's never been in the Medical Zone.

33:00.640 --> 33:04.340
They don't want any record regarding this incident

33:05.790 --> 33:09.530
and our government promised its full cooperation.

33:10.700 --> 33:12.530
About Captain Yoo Shi Jin,

33:12.530 --> 33:14.100
we'll respect your decision

33:14.720 --> 33:17.120
whether to reward or reprimand him.

33:18.830 --> 33:20.110
We’ll do that.

33:24.570 --> 33:26.920
Is Yoo Shi Jin still being detained?

33:26.920 --> 33:27.840
Yes, sir.

33:29.340 --> 33:32.490
Destroy the operation documents  and release Yoo Shi Jin.

33:32.490 --> 33:34.250
The disciplinary committee will be held as planned.

33:34.730 --> 33:37.170
Is he still going to be punished?

33:39.520 --> 33:40.970
Connect me to the Commander of the Taebaek Unit.

33:49.010 --> 33:50.510
Are there so many beans in Uruk?

33:52.660 --> 33:54.350
Why didn't you stop him?

33:56.240 --> 33:58.260
You were detained for two days in the storehouse

33:58.260 --> 34:02.710
and released. I prepared this tofu meal,

34:02.710 --> 34:05.930
with tofu stew on the right, and tofu and kimchi on the left.

34:06.280 --> 34:07.510
I carved a star as well.

34:07.510 --> 34:08.870
Released?

34:09.960 --> 34:10.900
No?

34:11.610 --> 34:14.159
Then…

34:16.030 --> 34:18.590
Cut loose? It’s action.

34:18.590 --> 34:20.860
I’m taking action, you idiot!

34:23.139 --> 34:24.040
What's wrong with him?

34:24.040 --> 34:25.550
I'll educate him more.

34:27.550 --> 34:29.730
Take this one first.

34:29.730 --> 34:31.820
You two can live thanks to Sergeant Choi.

34:37.550 --> 34:39.550
-Attention! -Sir!

34:40.690 --> 34:42.330
Let me say something here.

34:42.929 --> 34:44.469
We were under a state of emergency

34:44.469 --> 34:45.380
and my deputy was also absent,

34:45.380 --> 34:48.070
yet you did well.

34:48.900 --> 34:50.570
We're having a feast with tofu today,

34:51.440 --> 34:53.440
but I'll treat you to pork belly this weekend.

34:56.090 --> 34:57.940
Let's dig in. That's all.

34:57.940 --> 34:59.520
Thank you, sir!

35:07.990 --> 35:09.520
Why are you leaving?

35:10.470 --> 35:11.760
Didn't you come here to see me?

35:12.870 --> 35:15.010
Later. Go ahead and eat.

35:15.730 --> 35:19.360
No. Let's talk now.

35:36.840 --> 35:38.430
I thought you were a quack, but I was wrong.

35:39.380 --> 35:41.500
-You saved him. -You told me to save him.

35:41.820 --> 35:43.640
Wow. Such a good girl.

35:44.540 --> 35:45.840
You told me not to

35:45.840 --> 35:48.000
interfere with the medical services team.

35:48.660 --> 35:50.190
You don't let things go, do you?

35:50.490 --> 35:51.600
You've become quite chic

35:51.600 --> 35:52.580
overnight.

35:58.590 --> 36:02.120
If you feel gratitude, say thank me.

36:04.800 --> 36:07.340
Thank you for trusting me.

36:12.240 --> 36:13.290
Were you scared?

36:13.970 --> 36:15.330
To be honest, yes.

36:16.750 --> 36:17.740
Yes.

36:19.160 --> 36:20.630
Were you scared as well?

36:20.980 --> 36:23.650
This is a normal situation for a guy like me.

36:29.060 --> 36:31.970
And I've been meaning to tell you this,

36:32.000 --> 36:33.150
but I haven't had the chance.

36:34.110 --> 36:36.040
I said some doctors should be on TV.

36:36.550 --> 36:38.150
I didn't mean it.

36:39.550 --> 36:41.360
I hoped you'd forget about it.

36:42.460 --> 36:43.780
You weren't completely wrong.

36:44.630 --> 36:46.240
For the doctor who wanted to save a patient

36:46.240 --> 36:47.810
while in grave danger,

36:47.810 --> 36:48.510
it wasn't true..

36:48.810 --> 36:51.610
If you say so, then you tell the truth.

36:55.460 --> 36:57.900
You think they would really open fire?

37:02.760 --> 37:03.680
I don't want to hear it.

37:04.160 --> 37:07.110
Don't tell me… Don't tell me.

37:08.260 --> 37:09.350
Captain!

37:26.520 --> 37:30.210
Hello. Welcome, Dr. Kang and Captain Yoo!

37:32.190 --> 37:33.690
I heard that I was able to live because of your wise decision.

37:33.690 --> 37:35.790
Thanks to you,

37:35.790 --> 37:39.100
Allah allowed me more time to work.

37:39.470 --> 37:41.620
Thank you, in the name of Allah.

37:42.380 --> 37:44.230
You have a problem with your heart.

37:44.230 --> 37:46.320
You should avoid stress.

37:46.320 --> 37:48.920
Try to avoid hassles for a while

37:48.920 --> 37:50.690
and relax as much as possible.

37:53.330 --> 37:56.850
Indeed, doctors have no nationalities.

37:56.850 --> 37:58.500
You nag a lot.

38:00.920 --> 38:01.550
War is easy,

38:01.550 --> 38:02.860
but peace is troublesome.

38:03.620 --> 38:06.340
I guess that's why dictators live long.

38:11.840 --> 38:13.310
I think I can connect better with a soldier

38:13.310 --> 38:15.730
than a doctor.

38:18.090 --> 38:21.470
But I'll keep Dr. Kang's advice in mind.

38:21.880 --> 38:25.110
I think Allah has prepared something for me.

38:25.110 --> 38:27.370
It was an honor to treat

38:27.370 --> 38:28.650
a great man like you.

38:29.150 --> 38:34.480
I'm the one who should thank you. This is a gift.

38:42.110 --> 38:44.750
It's not just any business card.

38:44.750 --> 38:48.050
This card will save you in any bad situations,

38:48.050 --> 38:49.730
anywhere there are Arabs.

38:52.880 --> 38:57.960
Thank you so much, but can you give us one more?

38:57.960 --> 38:59.510
We're two people here.

38:59.760 --> 39:02.150
This might get wet.

39:14.700 --> 39:17.250
I guess this is some sort of free pass.

39:18.040 --> 39:19.870
Give me one. I want to check it out.

39:24.660 --> 39:25.900
I will drive.

39:27.200 --> 39:29.640
I will take the car for the day.

39:30.560 --> 39:32.850
How could you waste that card on renting a car?

39:32.850 --> 39:35.060
You could've bought a rental car company with it.

39:35.100 --> 39:36.500
Are you out of your mind?

39:38.330 --> 39:40.460
I didn't know you were such a reckless man.

39:41.110 --> 39:44.350
Don't you have any passion? They have lots of petroleum here.

39:44.350 --> 39:45.180
In their country,

39:45.180 --> 39:46.600
if you dig in the ground, you'll find petroleum.

39:46.600 --> 39:48.010
If you sell petroleum...

39:48.680 --> 39:51.380
Geez. We saved his life.

39:51.380 --> 39:54.250
He was willing to give us anything we wanted.

39:54.870 --> 39:58.490
You thought it’s wrong? I think it's worth it.

39:58.490 --> 40:00.000
What do you mean?

40:03.060 --> 40:05.480
I have two and a half hours of free time.

40:05.700 --> 40:10.170
At this speed, I can get there in half an hour.

40:11.340 --> 40:13.700
I have two hours to have a date with you.

40:15.380 --> 40:16.900
Crazy! Completely crazy!

40:16.900 --> 40:19.060
You wasted that card on a stupid date.

40:20.480 --> 40:23.550
Besides, who said I wanted a date with you?

40:23.550 --> 40:24.890
I didn't need your opinion.

40:26.420 --> 40:28.290
Let's have some coffee.

40:28.290 --> 40:29.610
Why didn't you ask?

40:39.270 --> 40:41.620
I still can't believe it.

40:43.720 --> 40:45.300
This is mine. Don't even think about touching it.

40:47.730 --> 40:48.680
What should I do with it?

40:49.530 --> 40:51.550
Should I open up a hospital there in Arab?

40:53.370 --> 40:55.220
I should have taken a picture with him.

40:55.580 --> 40:57.080
I could have put it on the wall of my clinic.

40:57.080 --> 40:58.330
I’ll be rich, right?

41:01.850 --> 41:04.100
Why did you become a doctor?

41:04.670 --> 41:06.120
I was good at school.

41:06.120 --> 41:07.180
I was a math genius.

41:07.690 --> 41:09.400
That's very persuasive.

41:10.370 --> 41:12.610
Doctors can make lots of money

41:12.610 --> 41:14.290
and I'd rather see money

41:14.290 --> 41:16.450
fall into my lap than chase it.

41:16.920 --> 41:20.930
I don't care what people say, but I work as much as I get paid.

41:20.930 --> 41:23.600
If I'm going to open up a hospital, I'd choose Gangnam.

41:27.980 --> 41:28.800
I don't care if you think

41:28.800 --> 41:30.490
I'm too material.

41:31.250 --> 41:34.790
Why do you pretend to be a terrible person?

41:38.500 --> 41:39.720
I reached the conclusion

41:39.720 --> 41:40.850
that I became a doctor to be rich.

41:42.000 --> 41:45.020
A lot of things happened after you left

41:45.060 --> 41:47.510
and I've changed a lot.

41:49.650 --> 41:52.910
However, you don't seem to have changed at all.

41:52.910 --> 41:55.030
I've become more handsome. Doesn't it?

41:57.030 --> 41:58.270
You're still a funny guy.

42:00.270 --> 42:02.430
You look prettier when you smile.

42:12.340 --> 42:12.990
Excuse me.

42:16.930 --> 42:17.640
Yes, I am.

42:19.380 --> 42:20.510
UN?

42:24.950 --> 42:26.470
Who?

42:36.570 --> 42:37.950
- I'm sorry, but... - Again?

42:39.010 --> 42:41.980
-Do you have to go? –Yes. Can you take the car back?

42:41.980 --> 42:44.630
This is always how our dates end,

42:44.630 --> 42:46.390
no matter we’re in Korea and even here.

42:47.570 --> 42:48.690
Where are you going?

42:49.620 --> 42:51.120
Can’t you tell me? Because of regulations?

42:52.000 --> 42:53.960
Am I not allowed to go there?

42:55.010 --> 42:56.980
It's not that you're not allowed,

42:58.670 --> 43:01.460
but it won't help me if I take you.

43:02.130 --> 43:03.940
Why are you so secretive about everything?

43:03.940 --> 43:05.640
Because what I do

43:07.440 --> 43:09.130
isn't helping our relationship.

43:11.280 --> 43:15.900
What if I still want to come along?

43:55.920 --> 43:57.650
Well done, guys.

43:58.520 --> 44:01.750
Get back to work.

44:02.400 --> 44:04.140
Oh, captain!

44:05.810 --> 44:07.120
-Look over there. - Mask!

44:07.120 --> 44:08.220
Okay, okay.

44:09.370 --> 44:13.030
Say kimchi. One, two, three!

44:13.490 --> 44:15.840
Kimchi!

44:40.680 --> 44:41.590
Let's go.

44:42.470 --> 44:43.720
We'd better get to work.

45:18.430 --> 45:21.560
It was a long day. Get some rest.

45:23.100 --> 45:24.360
Was he a fellow soldier?

45:26.730 --> 45:28.920
The funeral.

45:28.920 --> 45:30.070
You must have waited a long time.

45:31.100 --> 45:32.810
You could've asked me in the car.

45:37.080 --> 45:38.440
He was a fellow soldier.

45:39.330 --> 45:42.410
-How did he... -For trying to keep peace.

45:43.220 --> 45:45.710
So it means…

45:45.710 --> 45:47.800
Means that if you...

45:47.800 --> 45:52.930
Let's not talk about that.

45:55.470 --> 45:57.520
See? I told you.

45:57.520 --> 45:59.080
This isn't helping.

46:02.050 --> 46:02.920
Get some rest.

47:05.480 --> 47:06.460
Excuse me.

47:12.570 --> 47:15.660
I can't find Captain Yoo. Where is he?

47:15.660 --> 47:16.550
He was summoned to headquarters.

47:16.550 --> 47:19.070
For a disciplinary committee.

47:19.070 --> 47:21.580
A disciplinary committee? Why?

47:22.060 --> 47:24.240
I thought everything was settled.

47:24.240 --> 47:25.510
Maybe not.

47:26.370 --> 47:29.110
If you violate an order, you go to jail under martial law.

47:29.110 --> 47:31.180
You insisted to do the surgery.

47:31.180 --> 47:32.550
Why you didn't know?

47:39.220 --> 47:40.440
I repeat.

47:40.440 --> 47:42.780
We've decided that this committee can't

47:42.780 --> 47:44.870
officially punish you for insubordination.

47:44.870 --> 47:50.460
However, we hope you will never do that again.

47:50.460 --> 47:54.730
As for the battle of diffusing bombs on May 18th,

47:54.730 --> 47:57.210
you didn’t follow the order,

47:57.210 --> 47:59.450
so we’ve decided your pay will be cut for the next three months.

48:00.380 --> 48:01.580
Any objections?

48:01.810 --> 48:02.750
No, sir!

48:02.750 --> 48:05.840
You also won't be considered for

48:05.840 --> 48:07.650
a nominee for scheduled promotions next month.

48:07.650 --> 48:09.400
Any objections?

48:09.400 --> 48:10.490
No, sir!

48:10.490 --> 48:12.140
Good. Dismissed.

48:12.930 --> 48:13.820
Sir!

48:26.810 --> 48:28.030
What are you thinking?

48:28.030 --> 48:29.530
You shouldn't trip over something like this.

48:29.530 --> 48:30.890
How dare you!

48:32.900 --> 48:35.430
-When did you get here? -Yesterday.

48:36.000 --> 48:37.830
I heard that you were suffered.

48:38.230 --> 48:39.870
Don't admire me too much.

48:41.050 --> 48:44.500
Why didn't you open up a clinic in Gangnam

48:44.500 --> 48:46.620
instead of coming all the way here?

48:46.620 --> 48:50.110
How dare you! I'm an ambitious woman.

48:51.050 --> 48:52.760
I need to get military decorations.

48:53.880 --> 48:55.770
You caused a big stir this time.

48:55.770 --> 48:57.410
I might get one before you.

48:57.410 --> 49:00.050
Good for you.

49:02.220 --> 49:04.700
You're not looking for Sergeant Seo?

49:04.700 --> 49:06.720
You know he's gone back to Korea.

49:08.420 --> 49:10.280
I saw him at the airport.

49:10.280 --> 49:14.640
That explains it. Is everything okay?

49:15.020 --> 49:16.810
Whose side are you on?

49:17.640 --> 49:19.710
I'm always on my country's side.

49:23.910 --> 49:24.710
Thank you.

49:30.100 --> 49:31.630
She looks quite familiar.

49:31.630 --> 49:32.460
I agree.

49:32.630 --> 49:33.460
See you later.

49:35.660 --> 49:36.800
I'm the one responsible

49:36.800 --> 49:38.320
for the whole thing.

49:38.320 --> 49:40.860
Why does Captain Yoo have to take the fall all alone?

49:40.860 --> 49:41.880
He didn't do anything.

49:41.880 --> 49:43.160
Yes, he did.

49:43.680 --> 49:45.510
A soldier disobeyed his superior.

49:48.460 --> 49:50.260
You saved a life as a doctor.

49:50.260 --> 49:51.840
You did your job.

49:51.840 --> 49:54.410
It's different in the army.

49:54.410 --> 49:57.690
I was there. I can testify as a witness.

49:57.690 --> 50:00.250
I'll take responsibility for what I did wrong.

50:02.210 --> 50:03.890
Look, Doctor.

50:03.890 --> 50:05.500
This isn't a trial.

50:05.500 --> 50:07.040
You don't know what a reprimand is?

50:07.770 --> 50:09.450
He'll get a pay cut for three months

50:09.450 --> 50:11.410
and is excluded from the next promotion.

50:11.940 --> 50:13.600
How can you take responsibility for that?

50:18.670 --> 50:19.390
Sir!

50:21.490 --> 50:22.210
I'm sorry.

50:22.830 --> 50:23.940
Come here.

50:37.210 --> 50:38.340
Hey.

50:38.870 --> 50:40.110
What do you think you're doing?

50:43.120 --> 50:44.830
Why do you have to cause trouble?

50:44.830 --> 50:46.450
Cause trouble?

50:47.030 --> 50:48.340
Because of me, your life is...

50:48.340 --> 50:50.180
It's not because of you.

50:51.350 --> 50:52.000
Do you think I did it

50:52.000 --> 50:53.240
to impress a girl?

50:57.690 --> 50:59.930
Do you remember the gunshot

51:00.340 --> 51:02.270
you saw the day we met?

51:04.840 --> 51:07.150
On the first day I was commissioned to my platoon,

51:07.550 --> 51:09.670
one of the soldiers there told me

51:10.370 --> 51:13.240
a soldier's uniform is a shroud.

51:14.410 --> 51:17.830
When we die for our country somewhere far away from our home,

51:18.320 --> 51:20.320
that spot is our grave

51:20.820 --> 51:22.940
and our uniform is our shroud.

51:23.630 --> 51:25.910
You need to be mentally prepared for that.

51:26.980 --> 51:29.300
If you're mentally prepared for that,

51:29.300 --> 51:30.590
you’ll be honorable every moment.

51:30.590 --> 51:31.520
There's no reason why you shouldn’t be.

51:37.830 --> 51:39.910
I owe him my life.

51:42.300 --> 51:43.540
That's when

51:44.310 --> 51:46.530
I got that gunshot.

51:47.540 --> 51:50.560
Whether it's big or small, whatever decision I make

51:50.560 --> 51:51.500
I have to consider the honor, pride,

51:51.500 --> 51:54.460
and sense of duty to my fellow soldiers.

51:54.460 --> 51:56.130
That's what I did the other day.

51:56.130 --> 51:58.640
I made a decision while considering all that

51:58.640 --> 52:00.820
and I have no regrets.

52:01.370 --> 52:04.280
However, that doesn't mean

52:04.860 --> 52:07.680
that I can get away with disobeying my superiors.

52:12.180 --> 52:14.220
This is for the army to take care of.

52:14.220 --> 52:15.630
Can you please

52:18.830 --> 52:20.240
let it go?

52:23.680 --> 52:27.380
I'm sorry that

52:27.380 --> 52:29.590
my concern

52:31.900 --> 52:33.790
interfered with your job.

53:20.070 --> 53:21.890
Sir. Where are you?

53:21.890 --> 53:23.470
Have you arrived home safely?

53:24.960 --> 53:26.960
I'm on the road.

53:26.960 --> 53:28.400
On the road?

53:28.400 --> 53:30.690
Yes. On the road!

53:31.230 --> 53:33.030
I'm on my way to our barracks.

53:33.180 --> 53:35.270
You're on your way to barracks?

53:35.420 --> 53:38.280
Yes. I have a long way to go though.

53:38.280 --> 53:39.720
A road trip.

53:41.230 --> 53:42.440
Okay. Whatever.

53:43.750 --> 53:45.060
Have you seen Myung Joo?

53:45.060 --> 53:47.260
That's not important.

53:47.260 --> 53:50.240
I can't get promoted and I got a pay cut.

53:50.240 --> 53:52.380
I'm not surprised at all.

53:53.130 --> 53:55.020
How much money have you wasted for a woman?

53:56.020 --> 53:58.130
It's not because of a woman.

53:58.130 --> 54:01.030
I'm a soldier who put the safety of a citizen...

54:01.030 --> 54:03.050
That citizen is pretty.

54:03.050 --> 54:04.400
Geez!

54:05.860 --> 54:07.600
Did you call me to make me angry?

54:07.940 --> 54:09.240
That's not why I called,

54:09.240 --> 54:10.710
but since I called, I mentioned it.

54:12.720 --> 54:14.460
Did you see Myung Joo or not?

54:15.040 --> 54:18.770
Sergeant Seo, this is an international call.

54:20.960 --> 54:23.740
How much money are you wasting on a woman?

54:44.550 --> 54:45.270
Sir!

54:46.060 --> 54:48.320
Thank you.

55:04.580 --> 55:06.420
Check the kitchen counter.

55:07.480 --> 55:09.870
You got a pay cut and can't get promoted.

55:09.870 --> 55:13.760
I thought you might need a drink on a day like this.

55:25.370 --> 55:27.190
What do you want?

55:29.300 --> 55:30.530
I want some water.

55:31.640 --> 55:33.010
Then why are you leaving?

55:33.010 --> 55:33.970
Drink some water.

55:36.120 --> 55:37.830
I thought you might want to be alone.

55:37.830 --> 55:40.750
No. I want to be with you.

55:41.370 --> 55:42.510
I've said it many times.

55:44.290 --> 55:45.970
Don't go. Come here.

55:58.480 --> 56:01.010
How about some wine instead of water?

56:21.790 --> 56:23.360
I'm a soldier. I can't drink.

56:24.290 --> 56:25.870
Didn't you take it out to drink?

56:26.250 --> 56:27.400
I did.

56:28.450 --> 56:31.450
But there's a witness now.

56:39.280 --> 56:43.110
I'm sorry that I caused trouble earlier.

56:43.900 --> 56:45.320
I was going to apologize to you first.

56:46.550 --> 56:47.700
Let's call it even.

56:47.700 --> 56:48.620
You haven't.

56:54.310 --> 56:57.590
I was just kidding. I'm sorry.

56:58.500 --> 56:59.410
How did you get back?

56:59.410 --> 57:00.560
I ran.

57:01.800 --> 57:03.800
I'm a fast runner, you know.

57:05.940 --> 57:08.730
I saw you getting out of a car.

57:11.350 --> 57:12.280
You saw that.

57:14.370 --> 57:15.490
Then why did you ask?

57:15.490 --> 57:16.740
I wanted you to say something silly.

57:21.410 --> 57:22.930
You look good in your uniform.

57:24.550 --> 57:27.280
I'm sorry that you had to go

57:27.280 --> 57:29.660
to the disciplinary committee in that outfit.

57:31.730 --> 57:35.160
How do you know this was a uniform?

57:35.160 --> 57:36.700
How wouldn’t I?

57:37.070 --> 57:38.860
Women have fantasies about men in uniforms.

57:40.590 --> 57:42.400
That's why I became a soldier.

57:50.100 --> 57:51.240
Is it good?

57:51.550 --> 57:52.410
Yes.

57:54.070 --> 57:54.970
Do you enjoy drinking?

57:59.200 --> 58:01.580
I wanted to watch a movie

58:01.580 --> 58:03.450
and have a drink with you.

58:03.450 --> 58:06.260
It could've been the perfect date.

58:07.670 --> 58:09.270
Did you watch the movie?

58:09.430 --> 58:10.630
No.

58:10.630 --> 58:13.540
Why not?

58:13.540 --> 58:18.590
Because I wanted to watch it with someone.

58:20.370 --> 58:21.910
Then I thought.

58:22.430 --> 58:25.110
Next time when I choose a movie,

58:25.110 --> 58:28.110
I shouldn't pick a good one.

58:28.110 --> 58:29.790
That movie has ten million audiences.

58:29.790 --> 58:31.640
Every day there was an article of it.

58:33.360 --> 58:40.130
It reminded me of you often.

58:48.770 --> 58:50.290
Do you want a mouthful?

58:53.850 --> 58:55.710
I think I have a way.

59:25.220 --> 59:28.500
Next Episode

59:28.500 --> 59:30.100
Do you know exactly what

59:30.100 --> 59:32.530
Captain Yoo Shi Jin is up to?

59:32.530 --> 59:34.880
I went against someone.

59:34.880 --> 59:37.000
That’s the reason he wants me dead.

59:37.000 --> 59:38.600
Quick. It's collapsing.

59:39.510 --> 59:41.650
Help. Please help!

59:42.290 --> 59:44.710
Hang in there. I'll be there. I'll find you.

59:44.710 --> 59:46.310
Who's leaving?

59:46.310 --> 59:48.800
It's the Captain.

59:48.800 --> 59:50.650
Captain Yoo?
